testsuite.name: org.apache.openwhisk.common.ResizableSemaphoreTests

testcase.name: ResizableSemaphore should not allow to acquire, force or release negative amounts of permits
ResizableSemaphore should allow to acquire the defined amount of permits only
ResizableSemaphore should allow to release permits again
ResizableSemaphore should allow to resize permits when factor of reductionSize is reached during release
ResizableSemaphore should not give away more permits even under concurrent load
ResizableSemaphore should release permits even under concurrent load
